title: Oviri - The Wolf at the Door [1986] Donald Sutherland drama
description: Oviri [1986 - Denmark, France] also known as The Wolf at the Door Biography / Drama starring . . . . Donald Sutherland, Max von Sydow, Jean Yanne http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0091712/ A biographical film based on the life of French artist Paul Gauguin. In 1893, Gauguin arrived back in France from Tahiti with 66 canvases and 4 francs in his pocket. He was confident enough to suppose that his new paintings would take the art world by storm and transform his career. He held an exhibition at the Durand-Ruell Gallery in Paris. It was a fiasco and succeeded only in plunging him into debt. Nudity warning.
